snippet.title: Conic Sections: Parabolas, Part 1
snippet.description: Thanks to all of you who support me on Patreon. You da real mvps!   $1 per month helps!! :)  https://www.patreon.com/patrickjmt !! Conic Sections: Parabolas, Part 1.  In this video, I discuss a quick way to roughly sketch a parabola.  Nothing about directrix and focus in this video (look in part 2!). I simply find the vertex, x and y intercepts and do a quick graph.
